{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">MODIFICA RESOLUCION N&#xBA; 98 EXENTA, DE 2001</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  N&#xFA;m. 109 exenta.- Santiago, 6 de abril de 2001.- Visto: Lo dispuesto en la resoluci&#xF3;n exenta N&#xBA; 98 del 30 de marzo de 2001 de la Secretar&#xED;a Regional Ministerial de Transportes y Telecomunicaciones de la Regi&#xF3;n Metropolitana,</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  R e s u e l v o:</div><br><br></div>", "i": 8426539}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  1&#xBA; Sustit&#xFA;yase el cuadro contenido en el Resuelvo 1 de la resoluci&#xF3;n exenta N&#xBA; 98/2001, citada en el Visto, por el siguiente:</div><br><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Horario&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Tipos de veh&#xED;culos&nbsp; &nbsp;  Sentido de</div><div class=\"p\"> (lunes a viernes,&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Circulaci&#xF3;n</div><div class=\"p\"> excepto festivos)</div><br><div class=\"p\"> 07:30 - 10:00 horas&nbsp; * Buses Licitados&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Sur a Norte</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; * Taxis colectivos que</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; porten dispositivo</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; de idenficaci&#xF3;n</div><br><div class=\"p\"> 10:00 - 17:00 horas&nbsp; * Todo tipo de veh&#xED;culo Sur a Norte</div><br><div class=\"p\"> 17:00 - 21:00 horas&nbsp; * Buses Licitados&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Norte a Sur</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; * Taxis colectivos que</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; porten dispositivo</div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &